Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 蘭丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把津場木葵拐走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又為什麼放任她亂來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照黃金童子大人的吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要限制津場木葵的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你已經得到了結虹之傘和天狗的秘酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經很厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人魚之鱗和蓬萊玉枝 還有海味珍饌還沒準備好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人魚之鱗的話銀次馬上就能拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？丟給別人做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次看上去也進展艱難呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會拿到的 請您不用擔心
Comment: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:08.45,songtitle,,0,0,0,,「ウツシヨノユメ」 作詞：奈米、ZAI-ON，作曲、編曲：WEST GROUND，主唱：奈米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:29.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}黄昏の世で咲いた華は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:35.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}運命の糸を辿って　七色に輝き放つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:47.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}光照らし出すは　まだ見ぬ夢　永久の幻か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:55.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}隠り世から鳴る声　聴け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:02:00.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}闇夜を駈けろ　駈けろ　駈けろ　烈火の如く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:07.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}たとえこの身　燃え尽きようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:12.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}時を超え　千里の道を超え
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:18.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}願いも誓いも魂も抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:21.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}天上天下届くまで
Comment: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:29.79,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}在黃昏之世上綻開的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:35.20,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}追尋命運的絲線　閃耀釋放於七彩之上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:47.74,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}光芒照射出來　還未見過的夢想　是永恆的夢幻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:55.55,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}聽到來自隱世鳴響的　聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:02:00.85,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}奔馳越暗夜裡　奔跑吧　奔跑吧　如同烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:07.49,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}縱使這身軀　燃燒殆盡也會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:12.66,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}超越時光　超越千里之道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:18.33,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}無論願望或誓言還是靈魂都會懷抱著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:21.19,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}直達天上天下為止
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 這是天狗的秘酒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸大人出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是有要事要辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在舉行儀式前會嚴格保管的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想著要在他面前炫耀一番地說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笛聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是雷獸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌管雷電的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和黃金童子大人平起平坐的大貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷獸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳知道他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前在天神屋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..挺害打雷的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐妳也有害怕的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千萬別和他扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個享盡世間繁華
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,價值觀扭曲的享樂主義者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他反復無常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時候還會若無其事地做出殘忍的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明笛聲如此清澈動人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅是津場木史郎的孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是天神屋鬼神的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這讓人如何不提起興趣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒〜葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是才剛給天狗們做完料理嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要做什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵大人 那是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算做烤青花魚壽司和梅肉起司沙拉卷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜名就像是咒語一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是葵大人的晚飯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想給銀次送點宵夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狐狸哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來有段時間沒見到他了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像為了準備儀式而忙得不可開交呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛醬 這個能幫我烤一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經可以了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後我要努力成為有用的眷屬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個拿去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黃瓜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋃次 要是在房間就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的鼻子還是一如既往的靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 知道了 會分給你一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是讓我踉你過去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次你怎麼變成這...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在被污穢之物包裹住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,污穢之物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在用這座神社殘餘的神聖之力淨化中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要再靠近我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不害怕我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 一點也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼美麗的獸類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 銀次張開嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣...嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時都要花更多的時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上去那麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你好像瘦了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實最近可能沒怎麼好好吃東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來生活和工作都安排得很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是每次一有工作就會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 您教訓的對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 多吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是烤青花魚壽司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然葵小姐做的飯就是沁人心脾呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 尤其喜歡醋飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:07:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和銀次你第一次相遇的時候 你請我吃的就是稻荷壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是超級好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺很懷念呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海苔卷看起來也很好吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒猜到吧 這是起司哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是給淀子大人做東西時剩下的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文字燒的事情 銀次也聽說了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起司和和式料理的搭配
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要把這個加到新菜單裡面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕顏的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是...呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才你怎麼那麼虛弱呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐已經了解到什麼程度了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儀式的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這南方之地的詛咒的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分都是羽鳥先生告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這南方之地透過舉行儀式來避免災害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百年一次會有妖怪從海上來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 儀式需要用到五件寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次就是在收集寶物吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找的是人魚之鱗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人魚之鱗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人魚是非常稀少 而且高貴的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說現在已經滅絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也有傳言說她們去了常世
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那鱗片要怎麼得到呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮城遺址應該有遺留的鱗片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮城遺址？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是很久以前人魚們生活的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那裡聚集了強大且難纏的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便只是待上一下子也會被邪氣侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要去那麼危險的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近每個晚上都在去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後回來神社用神聖的靈力治癒身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這座神社究竟是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是折尾屋建立之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南方之地的八葉的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折尾屋建立之前...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說比蘭丸還早？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位八葉是一位名叫磯姬的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是女性…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是南方之地的磯男和最後一位人魚的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既高雅又美麗的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有神使般的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,額頭上有一塊能夠預知未來的水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預知...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人能看見未來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有著預見未來並且指引人們前進的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也被人們稱為「引導巫女」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引導巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 她也是我和蘭丸的養母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,養母...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時年幼的我和蘭丸無依無靠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人把我們帶回了這座神社
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人把我們培養成了守護獸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們終有一天能夠承擔儀式的重任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人帶著我們去了很多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集了很多關於海裡來的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及如何更加有效地舉行儀式的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從海上來的妖怪是怎樣的妖怪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身份不明的巨大的黑色詛咒凝聚體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都叫它「海坊主」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:11.77,NAME,NTP,0,0,0,,海坊主：日本傳說中一種居住在大海中的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海坊主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是往來於隱世和常世的海中魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在常世似乎被叫做「大太郎法師」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:20.69,NAME,NTP,0,0,0,,大太郎法師：日本傳說中的巨人。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然海坊主本身是非常溫順的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它會帶來龍捲風和颱風對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸和我都對自己的使命感到驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且尊愛著磯姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也深深地愛著這片南方之地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是三百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為某個人的背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儀式失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人預見了即將到來的不可避免的災難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 磯姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 請您不要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都是我的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人沉入了海裡的龍宮城遺址
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將災難引到了自己的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開了人世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今殘留在龍宮城的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是她為了守護南方之地而引到自己身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃金童子大人來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時還是天神屋女主人的黃金童子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡新建立了一家旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是折尾屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為折尾屋的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南方之地的才得以被守護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才拼命地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次為什麼會辭去折尾屋的工作呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知從何時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們兩個人的想法出現了分歧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在磯姬大人之後 蘭九繼任了八葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他希望折尾屋和南方之地發展壯大的願望過於強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都閉嘴聽我的吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是違逆的話就滾蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來去收購那家旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論用什麼手段都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要超越天神屋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓折尾屋成為隱世第一的旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也看不下去變成那樣的蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大老闆問我願不願意來天神屋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然要去天神屋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次 你要背叛我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我不能再繼續附和你的做法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是為了繼承磯姬大人的遺願而做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定還有其他的做法的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要放棄我們的使命嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會履行自己的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舉行儀式的時候我一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 現在就是你兌現諾言的時候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,儀式順利結束之後 你會回天神屋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,回到夕顏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之類的話 說不出口呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次 有我能做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想幫銀次的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:15:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 妳已經幫我們很多忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結虹之傘和天狗的秘酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 人魚之鱗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這件事不能和妳扯上關係 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是妳出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有什麼顏臉去見大老闆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回去吧 葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道..你去了龍宮城遺址嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都過了這麼久 你還是毫無進展
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明你的體質比我更容易被污穢侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:16:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼亂來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐 妳不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐 去折尾屋叫人過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 請為蘭丸做一些滋補的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼妳會在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維生素滿滿的蔬果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了一定可以恢復靈力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰要喝妳做的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是下毒了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沒禮貌的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你睡著的時候已經喝很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你昏倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和秀吉兩個人為了折尾屋忙得不可開交呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還需要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那個時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要儘快拿到人魚之鱗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 津場木葵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說過想幫銀次做點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那種情況下還偷聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我耳朵很靈的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴很臭就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是想做些只有妳才能做到的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人魚之鱗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮城遺址的邪氣對妖怪來說有毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是對人類卻沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想讓我去找人魚之鱗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳去找回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳重要的銀次就不用受污穢之苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 不是什麼壞事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 我去找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也肴條件的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 居然敢對我提條件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 等一切結束之後請把銀次還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個糾纏不休的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是銀次自己說不想回去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就沒辦法了 我會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我就同意這個交易
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我去找人魚之鱗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 還有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍...龍宮城遺址在哪裡呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受了一個不得了的任務呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我必須去做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好癢 好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總算回來了 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大老闆大人 莫非你一直在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很閒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在等小葵妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天妳很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想來犒賞一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的表情告訴我 又接了什麼麻煩的任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃瓜 黃瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是個不得了的任務呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒時間猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡沒底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這...真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是對妖怪來說...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和蘭丸 銀次他們是完全相反的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮城遺址的邪氣對我來說不影響
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全相反？真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說 就算有影響我也要去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和妻子一起面對困難也是丈夫的任務嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮城遺址是個什麼樣的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:00.00,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}月夜下的銀色巨獸
Comment: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:03.52,songtitle,,0,0,0,,「知らない気持ち 」作詞、作曲：シンリズム，編曲：シンリズム、高野勲，主唱：中島愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:20.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}ねぇ　どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:24.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}慣れない手で作った苦さを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:30.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}思い出して　笑ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:33.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}遠くで暮らし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:39.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}戸惑ってた　店先までも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.91,0:22:43.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}今では私の街
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:51.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}静かすぎて　眠れない夜でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:59.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}平気よ　見えない糸があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:04.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}ここがどこだって　構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:08.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}揺れる風景とその手を取り
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:10.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}まだ　ちょっとだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.25,0:23:15.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}知らないあなたの気持ちに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:19.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}そっと　寄り添いたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:24.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}迷ってしまわないように
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:20.08,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}喂　為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:24.96,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}回想起用不習慣的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:30.26,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}創造的苦澀　卻好像在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:33.67,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}在遠方的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:39.53,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}不知所措地　來到的店門前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.91,0:22:43.92,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}現在也已是我的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:51.69,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}即便是太過寧靜　而不成眠的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:59.11,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}也沒事唷　因為有著看不見的絲線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:04.63,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}就連這裡是哪裡　都不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:08.40,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}搖曳的風景並牽起那隻手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:10.24,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}還　只是有點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.25,0:23:15.07,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}不知道對於你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:19.19,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}想要悄悄地　靠近過去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:24.78,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}為了不會迷惘
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被黃瓜吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會成為有用的眷屬的
